 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Shed-skin:

    After each turn, this Pokémon 
  has a 33% of being cured of any 
  major status ailment.

  Marvel-scale:

    Whenever this Pokémon has a 
  major status ailment, it has 
  1.5× its Defense.

  This bonus does not count as 
  a stat modifier.


